1462
01:22:18.524 --> 01:22:22.987
We have to gather every bit
of evidence that we can


1463
01:22:23.029 --> 01:22:27.033
and then start trying to form
hypotheses and theories


1464
01:22:27.075 --> 01:22:29.535
as to what has transpired.

1465
01:22:29.577 --> 01:22:31.621
Did you notice
a Ryder truck?


1466
01:22:31.662 --> 01:22:34.291
The first real break
of the investigation,


1467
01:22:34.332 --> 01:22:36.376
