1476
01:23:02.568 --> 01:23:05.488
We immediately deployed
special agents


1477
01:23:05.529 --> 01:23:07.907
to that Ryder truck rental shop.

1478
01:23:07.949 --> 01:23:10.910
We learned that it had been
rented by a gentleman


1479
01:23:10.952 --> 01:23:13.621
