license


1480
01:23:13.663 --> 01:23:17.417
by the name of Robert Kling.

1481
01:23:17.459 --> 01:23:22.255
We had three principal witnesses
there inside the truck rental.


1482
01:23:22.297 --> 01:23:27.427
They described a military type
person, about six foot tall,


1483
01:23:27.469 --> 01:23:31.097
thin, close shaven.

1484
01:23:31.139 --> 01:23:35.059
They also believed that there
was a second person with him,


1485
01:23:35.101 --> 01:23:37.354
so we called these John Doe
number one


1486
01:23:37.395 --> 01:23:39.147
and John Doe number two.

1487
01:23:40.898 --> 01:23:45.820
Our agents flooded the area
of Junction City.


1488
01:23:48.198 --> 01:23:51.368
One particular agent went
to the Dreamland Motel,


1489
01:23:51.409 --> 01:23:54.496
