1501
01:24:31.282 --> 01:24:32.700
So that really got us.

1502
01:24:32.742 --> 01:24:34.618
We wanted to know
who Tim McVeigh was.


1503
01:24:34.660 --> 01:24:36.120
So what we did

1504
01:24:36.162 --> 01:24:38.664
