1506
01:24:40.833 --> 01:24:42.919
and try to find out if anybody
named Tim McVeigh


1507
01:24:42.960 --> 01:24:44.646
has been arrested anywhere
in the United States


1508
01:24:44.670 --> 01:24:45.838
in the recent past.

1509
01:24:48.716 --> 01:24:51.594
It turns out
that a highway patrolman


1510
01:24:51.635 --> 01:24:55.723
has arrested someone by the name
of Timothy McVeigh.


1511
01:24:55.765 --> 01:25:03.647
